
Online Store Website

This is a replica of a real-time online store website, built using Python and Flask. The website allows users to browse and purchase products, manage their cart, view their order history, and leave product reviews.

Features

User authentication: Users can create an account, log in, and log out. Passwords are hashed and stored securely in the database.
Product catalog: Users can browse a list of available products, view product details, and add items to their cart.
Shopping cart: Users can add and remove items from their cart, adjust quantities, and view the total cost of their order.
Checkout: Users can enter their shipping and billing information, and complete their order using a secure payment gateway.
Order history: Users can view their past orders and track their status.
Product reviews: Users can leave reviews for products they have purchased, and view reviews left by other customers.
